# ============================================================
# 8. Content Packの誤混入防止
# public版に残すContent Packを明示的に限定する
#
# 現在publicで許可するもの:
# - content/sample_minimal_pack/
# - content/sample_broken_missing_dialogue_pack/
#
# 新しい公開サンプルを追加する場合は、下に ! で明示的に許可する
# ============================================================

content/*
!content/sample_minimal_pack/
!content/sample_minimal_pack/**
!content/sample_broken_missing_dialogue_pack/
!content/sample_broken_missing_dialogue_pack/**


